heroSection.heroTaglineOne: Hello, we are And Us Agency.

aboutSection.homeAboutOne: As a partner to companies ranging from local startups to global consumer brands, we focus on four areas: Discover & strategize, brand development with a digital mindset, UX/UI design, and development.
aboutSection.homeAboutTwo: In everything we do, we are interested in how design and technology can elevate businesses, people and the communities around them.

approachSection.homeApproachOne: We’re not an advertising or even a marketing agency.
approachSection.homeApproachOneBolded: But if you want a label, ‘business partner’ comes close.
approachSection.homeApproachTwo: Our approach stems from our identity as equal parts creative agency, engineering firm, and consultancy. When we team up with like-minded brands, we become vested partners in their business, product, and services in order to drive incentivized growth.

articlesSection.articlesHeading: They say sharing is caring, right? We create articles to help give you insight and inspiration.
